    When you need to FTP 💾, but don't want to... Deploy 🚀 an FTPS server to Kubernetes or build 🧰 your own.当您需要 FTP 💾，但不想...部署 🚀 FTPS 服务器到 Kubernetes 或构建 🧰 你自己的。

    unFTP is an open-source FTP(S) (not SFTP) server aimed at the Cloud that allows bespoke extension through its pluggable authenticator, storage back-end and user detail store architectures. It aims to bring features typically needed in cloud environments like integration with proxy servers, Prometheus monitoring and shipping of structured logs while capitalizing on the memory safety and speed provided by its implementation language, Rust.unFTP 是一个针对云的开源 FTP(S) (不是 SFTP ) 服务器，它允许通过其可插入的身份验证器、存储后端和用户详细信息存储体系结构进行定制扩展。它旨在带来云环境中通常需要的功能，例如与代理服务器的集成、Prometheus 监控和结构化日志的传输，同时利用其实现语言 Rust 提供的内存安全性和速度。

    unFTP is first an embeddable library (libunftp) and second an FTPS server application (unFTP). You can run it out of the box, embed it in your app, craft your own server or build extensions for it.unFTP 首先是一个可嵌入库 (libunftp) ，其次是一个 FTPS 服务器应用程序 (unFTP)。您可以开箱即用，将其嵌入到您的应用程序中，制作您自己的服务器或为其构建扩展。

    unFTP tries to untangle you from old-school environments so you can move all the things, even FTP, to the cloud while your users still get that familiar FTP feeling.unFTP 试图将您从老式环境中解救出来，这样您就可以将所有东西 (甚至 FTP ) 移动到云中，而您的用户仍然可以获得熟悉的 FTP 感觉。

    libunftp - The FTPS librarylibunftp - FTPS 库

    libunftp is a Rust crate that you can use to build your own FTPS server with. You can extend it with your own storage back-ends or authentication back-ends.libunftp 是一个 Rust crate，你可以用它来构建你自己的 FTPS 服务器。您可以使用自己的存储后端或身份验证后端来扩展它。

    It runs on top of the Tokio asynchronous run-time and tries to make use of Async IO as much as possible.它在 Tokio 异步运行时之上运行，并尝试尽可能多地使用 Async IO。

    Feature highlights:功能亮点：

    • 39 Supported FTP commands and growing39 支持的 FTP 命令并不断增加
    • Ability to implement own storage back-ends能够实现自己的存储后端
    • Ability to implement own authentication back-ends能够实现自己的身份验证后端
    • Explicit FTPS (TLS)显式 FTPS (TLS)
    • Mutual TLS (Client certificates)相互 TLS（客户端证书）
    • TLS session resumptionTLS 会话恢复
    • Prometheus integration普罗米修斯整合
    • Structured Logging结构化日志记录
    • Proxy Protocol support代理协议支持
    • Automatic session timeouts自动会话超时
    • Per user IP allow lists每用户 IP 允许列表

    Known storage back-ends:已知的存储后端：

    • unftp-sbe-fs - Stores files on the local filesystemunftp-sbe-fs - 在本地文件系统上存储文件
    • unftp-sbe-gcs - Stores files in Google Cloud Storageunftp-sbe-gcs - 在谷歌云存储中存储文件

    Known authentication back-ends:已知的身份验证后端：

    • unftp-auth-jsonfile - Authenticates against JSON text.unftp-auth-jsonfile - 针对 JSON 文本进行身份验证。
    • unftp-auth-pam - Authenticates via PAM.unftp-auth-pam - 通过 PAM 进行身份验证。
    • unftp-auth-rest - Consumes an HTTP API to authenticate.unftp-auth-rest - 使用 HTTP API 进行身份验证。

    See the github page or the API Documentation for more details.有关详细信息，请参阅 github 页面或 API 文档。

    unFTP - The FTPS Server ApplicationunFTP - FTPS 服务器应用程序

    unFTP is a FTP(S) server written in Rust and built on top of libunftp and the Tokio asynchronous run-time. It is unlike your normal FTP server in that it provides:unFTP 是一个用 Rust 编写的 FTP(S) 服务器，构建在 libunftp 和 Tokio 异步运行时之上。它不同于您的普通 FTP 服务器，因为它提供：

    • Configurable Authentication (e.g. Anonymous, PAM or a JSON file).可配置的身份验证（例如匿名、PAM 或 JSON 文件）。
    • Configurable storage back-ends (e.g. GCS or filesystem)可配置的存储后端（例如 GCS 或文件系统）
    • An HTTP server with health endpoints for use for example in Kubernetes for readiness and liveness probes.具有健康端点的 HTTP 服务器，例如在 Kubernetes 中用于就绪和活动探测。
    • Integration with Prometheus for monitoring.与 Prometheus 集成以进行监控。
    • A proxy protocol mode for use behind proxies like HA Proxy and Nginx.在 HA Proxy 和 Nginx 等代理后面使用的代理协议模式。
    • Structured logging and the ability to ship logs to a Redis instance.结构化日志记录以及将日志发送到 Redis 实例的能力。

    With unFTP, you can present RFC compliant FTP(S) to the outside world while freeing yourself to use modern APIs and techniques on the inside of your perimeter.使用 unFTP，您可以向外界展示符合 RFC 标准的 FTP(S)，同时让您自己在内部使用现代 API 和技术。

    Binaries二进制文件

    Precompiled binaries for unFTP are available for Linux and macOS. On Linux you can choose between a statically linked image (no PAM integration) or a dynamically linked image with PAM integration:用于 unFTP 的预编译二进制文件可用于 Linux 和 macOS。在 Linux 上，您可以选择静态链接图像（无 PAM 集成）或具有 PAM 集成的动态链接图像：

    • unftp_x86_64-apple-darwin - macOSunftp_x86_64-apple-darwin - macOS
    • unftp_x86_64-unknown-linux-musl - Linux statically linked, no PAM support.unftp_x86_64-unknown-linux-musl - Linux 静态链接，不支持 PAM。
    • unftp_x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu - Dynamically linked with PAM support.unftp_x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu - 与 PAM 支持动态链接。

    To install with Curl:使用 Curl 安装：

    Linux (static, no PAM):Linux（静态，无 PAM）：

    curl -L https://github.com/bolcom/unFTP/releases/download/v0.14.0/unftp_x86_64-unknown-linux-musl \
  | sudo tee /usr/local/bin/unftp > /dev/null && sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/unftp

    Linux (dynamic with PAM support):Linux（具有 PAM 支持的动态）：

    curl -L https://github.com/bolcom/unFTP/releases/download/v0.14.0/unftp_x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu \
  | sudo tee /usr/local/bin/unftp > /dev/null && sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/unftp

    macOS:苹果系统：

    curl -L https://github.com/bolcom/unFTP/releases/download/v0.14.0/unftp_x86_64-apple-darwin \
  | sudo tee /usr/local/bin/unftp > /dev/null && sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/unftp

    From Source从源头

    You'll need Rust 1.45 (including cargo) or higher to build unFTP. Then: 您需要 Rust 1.45（包括 cargo）或更高版本来构建 unFTP。然后：

    cargo install unftp

    and find unftp in ~/.cargo/bin/unftp. You may want to add ~/.cargo/bin to your PATH if you haven't done so. The above merely creates the binary there, it won't start it as a service at the moment.并在 ~/.cargo/bin/unftp 中找到 unftp。如果您还没有这样做，您可能想将 ~/.cargo/bin 添加到您的 PATH 中。上面只是在那里创建二进制文件，目前不会将其作为服务启动。

    Arguments can be given to unFTP either via the command line or via environment variables. To show a list of available program arguments type the following:参数可以通过命令行或环境变量提供给 unFTP。要显示可用程序参数列表，请键入以下内容：

    unftp --help

    To run unFTP with everything set to the defaults:在所有设置为默认值的情况下运行 unFTP：

    unftp

    This will start unFTP:这将启动 unFTP：

    • with a filesystem back-end rooted at your OS temporary directory.文件系统后端植根于您的操作系统临时目录。
    • the FTP control channel bound to 0.0.0.0:2121 and the data channel range set to 0.0.0.0 ports 49152..65535FTP 控制通道绑定到 0.0.0.0:2121，数据通道范围设置为 0.0.0.0 端口 49152..65535
    • authentication being anonymous i.e. clients can specify any username and password身份验证是匿名的，即客户端可以指定任何用户名和密码

    Now serving data from your computer's temporary directory is not very useful so lets point it to a different directory by using the --root-dir argument. In addition, lets limit the data port range a bit:现在从您计算机的临时目录提供数据不是很有用，所以让我们使用 --root-dir 参数将其指向不同的目录。此外，让我们稍微限制一下数据端口范围：

    unftp \
  -v
  --root-dir=/home/unftp/data \
  --bind-address=0.0.0.0:2121 \
  --passive-ports=50000-51000 \

    ➜ unftp

    ➜ unftp -v

    Log shipping via Redis通过 Redis 进行日志传送

    In a cloud environment it is useful to send logs to a central location for analysis. unFTP can send structured logging in JSON format to a Redis instance. With a tool like Logstash this can then be processed further.在云环境中，将日志发送到中央位置进行分析很有用。 unFTP 可以将 JSON 格式的结构化日志记录发送到 Redis 实例。使用像 Logstash 这样的工具可以进一步处理。

    unFTP will use the RPUSH command to append logs at the tail of a list.unFTP 将使用 RPUSH 命令将日志附加到列表的尾部。

    Here is an example of configuring unFTP to send logs to a local Redis instance:以下是配置 unFTP 将日志发送到本地 Redis 实例的示例：

    unftp -v \
  --log-redis-host=localhost \
  --log-redis-port=6379 \
  --log-redis-key=logging

    The format of the JSON messages look like this:JSON 消息的格式如下所示：

     {
    "@timestamp": ${timeRFC3339},
    "@source_host": ${hostname},
    "@message": ${message},
    "@fields": {
       "level": ${levelLowercase},
       "application": ${appName}
       ... // logged field 1
       ... // logged field 2
       ...
   }
}

    Monitoring with Prometheus使用 Prometheus 进行监控

    To allow your Prometheus instance to scrape metrics from unFTP you have to enable unFTP's HTTP interface. This is done by specifying an HTTP bind address with the --bind-address-http argument or the UNFTP_BIND_ADDRESS_HTTP environment variable. For example if you do:要允许您的 Prometheus 实例从 unFTP 抓取指标，您必须启用 unFTP 的 HTTP 接口。这是通过使用 --bind-address-http 参数或 UNFTP_BIND_ADDRESS_HTTP 环境变量指定 HTTP 绑定地址来完成的。例如，如果您这样做：

    unftp \
  --bind-address=0.0.0.0:2121 \
  --bind-address-http=0.0.0.0:8080 \
  --root-dir=/home/unftp/data

    Your will have Prometheus metrics exposed on all IP addresses and port 8080 at endpoint http://../metrics. 您将在端点 http://../metrics 的所有 IP 地址和端口 8080 上公开 Prometheus 指标。

    Doing this will also expose an unFTP service information page at the HTTP root path.这样做还会在 HTTP 根路径处公开一个 unFTP 服务信息页面。

    Start by generating a self signed certificate首先生成自签名证书

    openssl req \
   -x509 \
   -newkey rsa:2048 \
   -nodes \
   -keyout unftp.key \
   -out unftp.crt \
   -days 3650 \
   -subj '/CN=www.myunftp.domain/O=My Company Name LTD./C=NL'

    The run unFTP, pointing it to the certificate and key. You can use the --ftps-required-on-control-channel setting to enforce TLS on the FTP control channel. In other words an FTP client will only be allowed to use FTP commands if it upgrades to a private TLS connection.运行 unFTP，将其指向证书和密钥。您可以使用 --ftps-required-on-control-channel 设置在 FTP 控制通道上强制执行 TLS。换句话说，如果 FTP 客户端升级到私有 TLS 连接，则只允许它使用 FTP 命令。

    ./unftp \
  --root-dir=/home/unftp/data \
  --ftps-certs-file=/home/unftp/unftp.crt \
  --ftps-key-file=/home/unftp/unftp.key \
  --ftps-required-on-control-channel=all

    Setting up Mutual TLS设置双向 TLS

    Create Server Root Key and Certificate:创建服务器根密钥和证书：

    openssl genrsa -out unftp_client_ca.key 2048
openssl req -new -x509 -days 365 \
	-key unftp_client_ca.key \
        -subj '/CN=unftp-ca.mysite.com/O=bol.com/C=NL' \
	-out unftp_client_ca.crt

    Create a client side key:创建客户端密钥：

    openssl genrsa -out client.key 2048

    Create a client side certificate signing request (CSR):创建客户端证书签名请求 (CSR)：

    openssl req -new -sha256 \
    -key client.key \
    -subj '/CN=unftp-client.mysite.com/O=bol.com/C=NL' \
    -reqexts SAN \
    -config <(cat /etc/ssl/openssl.cnf \
        <(printf "\n[SAN]\nsubjectAltName=DNS:localhost")) \
    -out client.csr

    Sign the certificate with our own CA使用我们自己的 CA 签署证书

    openssl x509 -req \
  -in client.csr \
  -CA unftp_client_ca.crt \
  -CAkey unftp_client_ca.key \
  -CAcreateserial \
  -extfile <(printf "subjectAltName=DNS:localhost") \
  -out client.crt \
  -days 1024 \
  -sha256

    Run unFTP pointing to the CA cert:运行指向 CA 证书的 unFTP：

    unftp \
  --root-dir=/home/unftp/data \
  --ftps-certs-file=/home/unftp/unftp.crt \
  --ftps-key-file=/home/unftp/unftp.key \
  --ftps-required-on-control-channel=all \
  --ftps-client-auth=require \
  --ftps-trust-store=/Users/xxx/unftp/unftp_client_ca.crt

    From another terminal: Connect with CURL, sending the client certificate:从另一个终端：使用 CURL 连接，发送客户端证书：

    curl -v \
  --insecure \
  --user 'test:test' \
  --ftp-ssl --ssl-reqd \
  --ftp-pasv --disable-epsv \
  --cacert unftp_client_ca.crt \
  --cert client.crt \
  --key client.key \
  --cert-type PEM \
  --pass '' \
  --tlsv1.2 \
  ftp://localhost:2121/

    You can run unFTP with a traditional file system back-end on a bare metal or virtual machine but if you're building your solutions in the cloud it would make sense to store your files in blob storage. unFTP comes with integration to Google Cloud Storage (GCS).您可以在裸机或虚拟机上使用传统文件系统后端运行 unFTP，但如果您在云中构建解决方案，则将文件存储在 blob 存储中是有意义的。 unFTP 集成了 Google Cloud Storage (GCS)。

    Using the GCS Back-end使用 GCS 后端

    You can enable the GCS backend by setting the storage back-end type (--sbe-type) to gcs. For storage authentication you can choose between workload identity and using a service account key file. For the former set the --sbe-gcs-service-account argument and for the latter the --sbe-gcs-key-file argument.您可以通过将存储后端类型 (--sbe-type) 设置为 gcs 来启用 GCS 后端。对于存储身份验证，您可以在工作负载身份和使用服务帐户密钥文件之间进行选择。对于前者设置 --sbe-gcs-service-account 参数，对于后者设置 --sbe-gcs-key-file 参数。

    The storage bucket name is chosen through --sbe-gcs-bucket and the root path inside the bucket through --sbe-gcs-root. 通过--sbe-gcs-bucket 选择存储桶名称，通过--sbe-gcs-root 选择桶内的根路径。

    Here is an example:这是一个例子：

    unftp \
  --sbe-type=gcs \
  --sbe-gcs-bucket=mybucket \
  --sbe-gcs-root=ftp-base \
  --sbe-gcs-key-file=/path/to/file

    Authentication setup身份验证设置

    Create a credentials file (e.g. credentials.json):创建凭证文件（例如 credentials.json）：

    [
  {
    "username": "alice",
    "password": "12345678"
  },
  {
    "username": "bob",
    "password": "secret"
  }
]

    unftp \
    --auth-type=json \
    --auth-json-path=credentials.json

    Generating secure passwords生成安全密码

    We provide a tool that generates a secure password for you.我们提供了一个为您生成安全密码的工具。

    Generating a secure password is as simple as this:生成安全密码就这么简单：

    ➜ docker run -ti bolcom/unftp-key-generator -u

Enter username or press ENTER to finish: hannes
Enter password or press ENTER to generate one:
Generated password: 4?KH[FN=W@bztq%[
[
  {
    "username": "hannes",
    "pbkdf2_salt": "+uhutJYSS7Y=",
    "pbkdf2_key": "sXdS1w0cH+bsNLKwW/Mek0hGXoJr+hrBJ1AjkubePiM=",
    "pbkdf2_iter": 500000
  }
]

    Then add it to the JSON credentials file. Notice the use of the pbkdf2_salt, pbkdf2_key and pbkdf2_iter fields instead of the password field.然后将其添加到 JSON 凭据文件。请注意使用 pbkdf2_salt、pbkdf2_key 和 pbkdf2_iter 字段而不是密码字段。

    [
  {
    "username": "alice",
    "password": "12345678"
  },
  {
    "username": "bob",
    "password": "secret"
  },
  {
    "username": "carol",
    "pbkdf2_salt": "Hp1WZRnzOUM=",
    "pbkdf2_key": "BOipkps/qYxlMLiuFcRjYUKivclvVXsc8f0T2pIvG6U=",
    "pbkdf2_iter": 500000
  }
]

    For more advanced usage see the documentation of the unftp_auth_jsonfile crate. The key generator tool also have advanced options that you can see by running the container with the -h option i.e.有关更高级的用法，请参阅 unftp_auth_jsonfile crate 的文档。密钥生成器工具还具有高级选项，您可以通过使用 -h 选项运行容器来查看这些选项，即

    docker run -ti bolcom/unftp-key-generator -h

    Per-User Settings每用户设置

    To do per-user settings you can expand the above-mentioned JSON file to also include some per user settings:要进行针对每个用户的设置，您可以扩展上述 JSON 文件以包含一些针对每个用户的设置：

    [
  {
    "username": "alice",
    "password": "12345678",
    "vfs_perms": ["-mkdir","-rmdir","-del","-ren", "-md5"],
    "root": "alice",
    "account_enabled": true
  },
  {
    "username": "bob",
    "password": "secret",
    "client_cert": {
      "allowed_cn": "bob-the-builder"
    }
  },
  {
    "username": "vincent",
    "root": "vincent",
    "vfs_perms": ["none", "+put", "+md5"],
    "client_cert": {}
  }  
]

    And let unFTP point to it:并让 unFTP 指向它：

    unftp \
    --auth-type=json \
    --auth-json-path=users.json \
    --usr-json-path=users.json \
    ...

    In the above configuration we use:在上面的配置中，我们使用：

    • vfs_perms - Specifies what permissions users can have. Alice cannot create directories, remove them, delete files nor calculate the md5 of files. Bob can do everything while Vincent can only do uploads and calculate md5 files. Valid values here are "none", "all", "-mkdir, "-rmdir, "-del","-ren", "-md5", "-get", "-put", "-list", "+mkdir", "+rmdir", "+del", "+ren", "+md5", "+get", "+put" and "+list".vfs_perms - 指定用户可以拥有的权限。 Alice 无法创建目录、删除目录、删除文件或计算文件的 md5。 Bob 可以做任何事情，而 Vincent 只能做上传和计算 md5 文件。此处的有效值为“none”、“all”、“-mkdir”、“-rmdir”、“-del”、“-ren”、“-md5”、“-get”、“-put”、“-list”、 “+mkdir”、“+rmdir”、“+del”、“+ren”、“+md5”、“+get”、“+put”和“+list”。
    • root - Sets the home directory of the user relative to the storage back-end root. Alice can only see files inside $SB_ROOT/alice, Bob can see all files and Vincent thinks $SB_ROOT/vincent is the FTP root similar to Alice.root - 设置用户相对于存储后端根目录的主目录。 Alice 只能看到 $SB_ROOT/alice 里面的文件，Bob 可以看到所有文件，Vincent 认为 $SB_ROOT/vincent 是和 Alice 类似的 FTP root。
    • account_enabled - Allows to disable the user's account completelyaccount_enabled - 允许完全禁用用户的帐户
    • client_cert - Allows specifying whether a client certificate is required and how to handle it. Alice logs in with normal user/password authentication. No client certificate needed. Bob needs to provide a valid client certificate with common name (CN) containing, 'bob-the-builder' and also needs to provide a password. Vincent can do passwordless login when providing a valid certificate.client_cert - 允许指定是否需要客户端证书以及如何处理它。 Alice 使用正常的用户/密码身份验证登录。不需要客户端证书。 Bob 需要提供包含“bob-the-builder”的通用名称 (CN) 的有效客户端证书，还需要提供密码。 Vincent 可以在提供有效证书的情况下进行无密码登录。

    Compressing configuration files压缩配置文件

    Since unFTP v0.14.0, the auth-json-path and usr-json-path also support JSON files that are compressed with gzip, or gzip+base64-encoded.自 unFTP v0.14.0 起，auth-json-path 和 usr-json-path 还支持使用 gzip 压缩或 gzip+base64 编码的 JSON 文件。

    This comes in handy when your storage is limited, and you have many users in your configuration. When running unFTP as a container in a Kubernetes Pod for example. In such a setup you may have your JSON credentials file mapped into your pod via a ConfigMap or a Secret. The size of these resources is limited. By compressing the file you can grow to a larger number of users before you technically require an external database solution.当您的存储空间有限并且您的配置中有很多用户时，这会派上用场。例如，在 Kubernetes Pod 中将 unFTP 作为容器运行时。在这样的设置中，您可以通过 ConfigMap 或 Secret 将您的 JSON 凭证文件映射到您的 pod。这些资源的大小是有限的。通过压缩文件，您可以在技术上需要外部数据库解决方案之前增加到更多的用户。

    For systems working alongside unFTP it might be useful to know of FTP related events happening. For this unFTP supports integration with Google Pub/Sub.对于与 unFTP 一起工作的系统，了解 FTP 相关事件的发生可能很有用。为此，unFTP 支持与 Google Pub/Sub 集成。

    Enabling the Pub/Sub integration启用发布/订阅集成

    You can enable the unFTP Pub/Sub notifier by specifying the --ntf-pubsub-project and --ntf-pubsub-topic arguments. 您可以通过指定 --ntf-pubsub-project 和 --ntf-pubsub-topic 参数来启用 unFTP Pub/Sub 通知程序。

    NOTE: Currently authentication with workload identity is the only supported authentication mechanism.注意：目前，使用工作负载身份进行身份验证是唯一受支持的身份验证机制。

    Here is an example:这是一个例子：

    unftp \
  --ntf-pubsub-project="my-project" \
  --ntf-pubsub-topic="unftp-events"

    The Message Format消息格式

    The Pub/Sub message sent by unFTP contains meta data (attributes) as shown below and a body in JSON format.unFTP 发送的 Pub/Sub 消息包含如下所示的元数据（属性）和 JSON 格式的正文。

    Message attributes:消息属性：

    Message attributes can be used to filter messages messages such that when you receive messages from a subscription with a filter, you only receive the messages that match the filter. unFTP only specifies an eventType attribute:消息属性可用于过滤消息 messages，这样当您从带有过滤器的订阅中接收消息时，您只会收到与过滤器匹配的消息。 unFTP 只指定一个 eventType 属性：

    Key钥匙Value价值Description描述
    eventType事件类型One of: 之一：

    - startup - 启动
    - login - 登录
    - logout - 登出
    - get - 得到
    - put - 放
    - delete - 删除
    - makeDir - 制作目录
    - rename - 改名
    - removeDir- 删除目录

    		Indicates the type of event指示事件的类型

    Message Body邮件正文

    The message body is a JSON object with these fields:消息正文是一个具有以下字段的 JSON 对象：

    Field场地Type类型Explanation解释
    source_instance源实例string细绳This is the name of the unFTP instance as set by the --instance-name variable. Default is 'unFTP'.这是由 --instance-name 变量设置的 unFTP 实例的名称。默认为“unFTP”。
    hostname主机名string细绳The operating system host name where unFTP is running.运行 unFTP 的操作系统主机名。
    payload有效负载Payload Object载荷对象More detail on the specific event type. See below.有关特定事件类型的更多详细信息。见下文。
    username用户名string细绳The name used during FTP login or "unknown" if not logged in yet.FTP 登录期间使用的名称，如果尚未登录则为“未知”。
    trace_idtrace_idstring细绳A number that uniquely identifies the FTP connection or session.唯一标识 FTP 连接或会话的数字。
    sequence_number序列号number数字Identifies the position of the event in the sequence of events for the connection.标识事件在连接事件序列中的位置。

    The Payload Object (payload field) can be one of:有效载荷对象（有效载荷字段）可以是以下之一：

    • Startup启动
    • Login登录
    • Logout登出
    • Get得到
    • Put放
    • Delete删除
    • MakeDir制作目录
    • Rename改名
    • RemoveDir删除目录

    All of them are of type JSON object. Examples of their format are shown below.它们都是 JSON 对象类型。它们的格式示例如下所示。

    Example Events示例事件

    Startup Event:启动事件：

    {
   "source_instance":"unFTP",
   "hostname":"MYMAC-XYZ",
   "payload":{
      "Startup":{
         "libunftp_version":"0.18.3",
         "unftp_version":"v0.14.0"
      }
   }
}

    Login Event:登录事件：

    {
   "source_instance":"unFTP",
   "hostname":"MYMAC-XYZ",
   "payload":{
      "Login":{ }
   },
   "username":"hannes",
   "trace_id":"0xe25ceb1d960303f3",
   "sequence_number":1
}

    Logout Event:注销事件：

    {
   "source_instance":"unFTP",
   "hostname":"MYMAC-XYZ",
   "payload":{
      "Logout":{ }
   },
   "username":"hannes",
   "trace_id":"0xe25ceb1d960303f3",
   "sequence_number":2
}

    Get Event (FTP RETR):获取事件（FTP RETR）：

    {
   "source_instance":"unFTP",
   "hostname":"MYMAC-XYZ",
   "payload":{
      "Get":{
         "path":"hello.txt"
      }
   },
   "username":"hannes",
   "trace_id":"0x687ee52555459a9c",
   "sequence_number":2
}

    Make Directory Event (FTP MKD):创建目录事件 (FTP MKD)：

    {
   "source_instance":"unFTP",
   "hostname":"MYMAC-XYZ",
   "payload":{
      "MakeDir":{
         "path":"/x"
      }
   },
   "username":"hannes",
   "trace_id":"0x687ee52555459a9c",
   "sequence_number":3
}

    Rename Event (FTP RNFR and RNTO):重命名事件（FTP RNFR 和 RNTO）：

    {
   "source_instance":"unFTP",
   "hostname":"MYMAC-XYZ",
   "payload":{
      "Rename":{
         "from":"/x",
         "to":"/y"
      }
   },
   "username":"hannes",
   "trace_id":"0x687ee52555459a9c",
   "sequence_number":4
}

    Put Event (FTP STOR):放置事件（FTP STOR）：

    {
   "source_instance":"unFTP",
   "hostname":"MYMAC-XYZ",
   "payload":{
      "Put":{
         "path":"x.yaml"
      }
   },
   "username":"hannes",
   "trace_id":"0x687ee52555459a9c",
   "sequence_number":5
}

    To protect your FTP server against password guessing attacks, you can enable a "Failed logins policy". This temporarily blocks the account if too many failed logins occur.为了保护您的 FTP 服务器免受密码猜测攻击，您可以启用“登录失败策略”。如果登录失败次数过多，这会暂时阻止该帐户。

    You can start up unFTP with the default failed logins policy:您可以使用默认的失败登录策略启动 unFTP：

    unftp --failed-logins-policy

    By default, 3 subsequent unsuccessful login attempts block further login attempts for that user orginating from that source IP for 5 minutes.默认情况下，连续 3 次不成功的登录尝试将阻止该用户从该源 IP 发起的进一步登录尝试 5 分钟。

    How to adjust these parameters and the default policy is explained in the sections below.如何调整这些参数和默认策略将在以下部分进行说明。

    Adjust max attempts and duration调整最大尝试次数和持续时间

    To change this to block after 5 attempts instead of 3:要将其更改为在尝试 5 次而不是 3 次后阻止：

    unftp --failed-logins-policy --failed-max-attempts 5

    To change this to block for 30 minutes (1800 seconds) instead of 5 minutes (300 seconds):要将其更改为阻止 30 分钟（1800 秒）而不是 5 分钟（300 秒）：

    unftp --failed-logins-policy --failed-expire-after 1800

    Choose another policy选择其他政策

    By default, the temporary block applies to the combination of username and source IP. When an attacker is blocked by this policy, attempts to use other accounts, or attempts from different source IPs can still succeed. You can adjust this behavior by blocking based on source IP or username instead.默认情况下，临时阻止适用于用户名和源 IP 的组合。当攻击者被此策略阻止时，尝试使用其他帐户或来自不同源 IP 的尝试仍然可以成功。您可以通过基于源 IP 或用户名进行阻止来调整此行为。

    Block by source IP instead of both IP and username:按源 IP 而不是 IP 和用户名阻止：

    unftp --failed-logins-policy ip

    Block by username instead of both IP and username:按用户名而不是 IP 和用户名阻止：

    unftp --failed-logins-policy user

    Be aware that user level -only blocking may also affect legitimate login attempts.请注意，仅限用户级别的阻止也可能会影响合法的登录尝试。

    Example例子

    Block an attacker based on source IP for 30 minutes after 5 unsuccessful login attempts:在 5 次登录尝试失败后，根据源 IP 阻止攻击者 30 分钟：

    unftp \
  --failed-logins-policy ip \
  --failed-max-attempts 5 \
  --failed-expire-after 1800

    You can download pre-made docker images from docker hub e.g.:您可以从 docker hub 下载预制的 docker 镜像，例如：

    docker pull bolcom/unftp:v0.14.0-alpine
docker pull bolcom/unftp:v0.14.0-alpine-istio
docker pull bolcom/unftp:v0.14.0-scratch

    Example running unFTP in a Docker container:在 Docker 容器中运行 unFTP 的示例：

    docker run \
  -e ROOT_DIR=/ \
  -e UNFTP_LOG_LEVEL=info \
  -e UNFTP_FTPS_CERTS_FILE='/unftp.crt' \
  -e UNFTP_FTPS_KEY_FILE='/unftp.key' \
  -e UNFTP_PASSIVE_PORTS=50000-50005 \
  -e UNFTP_SBE_TYPE=gcs \
  -e UNFTP_SBE_GCS_BUCKET=the-bucket-name \
  -e UNFTP_SBE_GCS_KEY_FILE=/key.json \
  -p 2121:2121 \
  -p 50000:50000 \
  -p 50001:50001 \
  -p 50002:50002 \
  -p 50003:50003 \
  -p 50004:50004 \
  -p 50005:50005 \
  -p 8080:8080 \
  -v /Users/xxx/unftp/unftp.key:/unftp.key  \
  -v /Users/xxx/unftp/unftp.crt:/unftp.crt \
  -v /Users/xxx/unftp/the-key.json:/key.json \
  -ti \
  bolcom/unftp:v0.14.0-alpine
